{"tid":1746913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普：繼續選副總統彭斯為明年競選搭擋","createTime":"2019-11-23T03:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T06:52:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":200,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"55a021a45d48c298b14dace6d009c38879e97acd","tid":1746913,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2019/10/25/c3b02bf7b83c447c45acf1f1cfbc9832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2Fc3b02bf7b83c447c45acf1f1cfbc9832.jpg&h=fd826e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國副總統彭斯。(美聯社/達志影像)<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普(Donald Trump)在美東時間22日表示，他將會繼續以副總統彭斯(Mike Pence)做為2020年總統大選的競選搭擋。<br />\n<br />\n川普今天在接受福斯新聞頻道(Fox News Channel)的「福斯與朋友們」(Fox &amp; Friends)節目訪問時，<span style=\"color: red;\">對於選擇彭斯為連任競選搭擋表示：「他是我的兄弟，他是我的朋友。」</span><br />\n<br />\n川普在訪談中，提及前美國常駐聯合國代表海利(Nikki Haley)時表示，他也很棒，但是彭斯已完成「很出色的工作」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2042450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2042450&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvghZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=ad2f7369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2042450</a>"},{"pid":"37615ddf61d1dd5bb18fc66aa689743c0853dd32","tid":1746913,"uid":27946,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"最佳組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7d365593b7bf9c3d80a82902346896713d7ce0","tid":1746913,"uid":184679,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"Xi is my best friend <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdb3bbce8cfe1cb27966382690a364ec387a97f","tid":1746913,"uid":71144,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:59:56.000Z","msg":"雖然基味濃 但係彭斯的確係有料到<b